These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, chess
City: edinburgh, hannover, rome
1. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Hobby      | skydiving | chess | traveling |
| City   | hannover     | edinburgh    | rome   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
House: modern, art-deco, farmhouse
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, egyptian
1. the modern house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the egyptian is between the german and the modern house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| House   | modern    | farmhouse        | art-deco |
| Nationality     | russian | egyptian | german         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, polish, australian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the german##1
2. the german is between the person who's birthday is in november and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Nationality   | polish | german     | australian |
| Birthday        | november  | july | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, bellflower
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the person who growspoppy is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Flower   | aconite  | bellflower     | poppy |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | mirinda | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, cherry, plum
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, bridge
1. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing bridge and the person playing chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Food   | cherry | plum     | peach |
| Game     | bridge    | monopoly | chess    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
House: victorian, farmhouse, gothic-revival
City: nizza, liverpool, boston
1. the person traveling to nizza is between the gothic-revival house and the victorian house##2
2. the victorian house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| House   | victorian  | farmhouse   | gothic-revival        |
| City         | liverpool | nizza | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, coral, chestnut
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, bartender, lawyer
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the paramedic is between the person who likes chestnut and the bartender##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Color          | coral  | light-blue  | chestnut |
| Job   | bartender | paramedic | lawyer     |

