.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, cola
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, reading, fishing
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking cola##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | cola   | lemonade  | milk  |
| Hobby   | gardening | reading | fishing |

