.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, brown, mauve
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, techno
1. the fan salsa is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
2. the fan salsa is between the person who likes mauve and the fan jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Color       | mauve | lilac | brown  |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | salsa        | jazz |

