2. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | filmmaking   | camping   |
| City         | venice | london | san-francisco |

