.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, cooking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, prince, oliveros
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | gardening | cooking | magic-tricks |
| Cigar   | prince    | oliveros | tiparillo   |

