.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, family, adventure
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, turquise, lilac
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who likes turquise##2
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | adventure | family   | disaster |
| Color   | lilac  | white | turquise   |

 